dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2015. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Waupaca_Addresses_2015.gdb. [The layer is primarily used as base reference data for digital mapping, emergency response, address centerline geocoding, and consistency checks with other parcel-based information.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. Best available date of this dataset is 5/12/2015. For online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.waupaca.wi.us/landinformation/Data.aspx [This file is rarely (if ever) fully representative of a dynamically changing landscape, the best that can be expected is data relative to a specific point in time.]
